data.description: Welcome to 203 Pocosin Court! Priced under market value! This home has the space your looking for PLUS a new HVAC system and a Buyers Use as They Choose of $5000!!! This home features four bedrooms, a loft area, formal living room, family room, eat-in kitchen and two and half baths! Its situated on a cul-de-sac and .60 acres. Outside of city limits so save monthly but still only minutes to what you need.
